  "contentFields": [
    {
      "contentFieldValue": {
        "data": "<p><iframe allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/YdDQKAokylo?si=AGbdun997vyITYW2\" title=\"YouTube video player\" width=\"100%\"></iframe></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">To activate your Self-Hosted Liferay DXP or Portal product Administrators should navigate to the Product Activation tab on the left sidebar navigation in <a href=\"https://support.liferay.com/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #0041be; text-decoration: underline; background-color: #ffffff; font-family: ' Source Sans Pro' , ' Source Serif Pro' , -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, ' Segoe UI' , Roboto, ' Helvetica Neue' , Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal;\" target=\"_blank\">Customer Portal</a> and select </span><strong>DXP </strong><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">or </span><strong>Portal</strong><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">.</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Click on the </span><strong>Actions </strong><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">button in the right corner and select </span><strong>Generate New.</strong></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">You will then be prompted to fill out the following:&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li aria-level=\"1\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Product</span></li>\n\t<li aria-level=\"1\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Version</span></li>\n\t<li aria-level=\"1\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Key Type</span>\n\t<ul>\n\t\t<li aria-level=\"1\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Physical or Virtual Server Production, Non-Production, or Backup Key Types:</span>\n\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t<li aria-level=\"3\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Subscription Term&nbsp;</span></li>\n\t\t\t<li aria-level=\"3\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">For each instance to be activated</span>\n\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t<li aria-level=\"3\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Host-Name&nbsp;</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li aria-level=\"3\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">IP Address&nbsp;</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li aria-level=\"3\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">MAC Address</span></li>\n\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t</li>\n\t\t</ul>\n\t\t</li>\n\t\t<li aria-level=\"2\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">For Virtual Cluster Key Types:</span>\n\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t<li aria-level=\"3\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Environment Name&nbsp;</span></li>\n\t\t\t<li aria-level=\"3\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Description</span></li>\n\t\t\t<li aria-level=\"3\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Cluster Nodes</span></li>\n\t\t</ul>\n\t\t</li>\n\t</ul>\n\t</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Liferay SaaS and Liferay PaaS deployments do not require a separate product activation key to deploy. However, you can use <a href=\"https://support.liferay.com/w/how-do-i-download-a-developer-key\">Liferay Developer Keys</a> for local testing and development.</span></p>\n\n<h2 id=\"h_01HDKZTQS127SJPM2SDB24XJ4R\">Related Articles</h2>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li aria-level=\"1\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><a href=\"https://support.liferay.com/w/how-do-i-download-my-liferay-dxp-portal-activation-keys\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">How do I download my Liferay DXP/ Portal Activation Keys?&nbsp;</span></a></li>\n\t<li aria-level=\"1\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><a href=\"https://support.liferay.com/w/how-do-i-view-all-generated-liferay-dxp-portal-activation-keys\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">How do I view all Liferay DXP/Portal generated activation keys?&nbsp;</span></a></li>\n\t<li aria-level=\"1\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><a href=\"https://support.liferay.com/w/can-i-download-a-file-with-all-my-activation-keys\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Can I download a file with all my activation keys?</a>&nbsp;</span></li>\n\t<li aria-level=\"1\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><a href=\"https://learn.liferay.com/kb-article/deploying-activation-keys\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Deploying Activation Keys</span></a></li>\n\t<li aria-level=\"1\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><a href=\"https://support.liferay.com/w/activation-keys-faq-for-liferay-dxp-and-liferay-commerce\">Activation Keys FAQ</a></li>\n</ul>"
      },
